data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Mulvane, Kansas! This charming property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Additionally, the basement features 1 bonus room, offering versatile spaces that can be customized to suit your needs – whether it's a home office, gym, or entertainment area. The heart of this home is the inviting living room, complete with a gas fireplace that adds warmth and coziness. For those who love outdoor living, the property features a covered patio, providing a serene space to enjoy the fresh air and relax. The 10x28 covered deck, attached to the expansive family room, is a highlight of this home. It's the perfect spot for hosting gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding while taking in the scenic surroundings.  Located in the excellent Mulvane school district, this home ensures that educational opportunities are easily accessible for your family. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home – a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm in the heart of Mulvane.  Schedule your showing today!
